org.jboss.windup.reporting.model

Interface ApplicationReportModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ReportModel, com.tinkerpop.frames.VertexFrame, WindupVertexFrame
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IgnoredFilesReportModel

    public interface ApplicationReportModel
extends ReportModel
    These reports are directly associated with an application, and that application's project model. These can include things like an Application Overview report (with various hints, etc) as well as more specific reports (hibernate reports, ejb reports, classloading reports, etc).
    Author:
    jsightler
